{"tid":913731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"塵爆前一刻可以有動作減少傷害架","createTime":"2018-11-23T15:35:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T05:07:20.000Z","uid":14941,"like":23,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3895e7c35a90f498acf4770ea6790069dbc4b6f0","tid":913731,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T15:35:15.000Z","msg":"塵爆係由於麵粉燃燒<br />\n<br />\n只要見到面前著火既一瞬大力呼氣，可以吹散初起之火種，同時雙手在面前周圍不停撥，造成亂流，散走面前既麵粉，就可以減低燒面既傷害<br />\n<br />\n如果驚反應唔夠快，可以馬上旋轉身體，不停自轉，令麵粉同火星沾唔到上身，仲可以旋轉中加入張開再收回手臂既動作，用向心力去分離身體同空氣中既麵粉<br />\n<br />\n呢啲常識應該加以普及啦"},{"pid":"d122729a527ef095e4c23e23d4fdcd1140f74072","tid":913731,"uid":195994,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T15:36:42.000Z","msg":"你認真就輸了"},{"pid":"4007cfd1a57585e9bec64d7b28131999c9de8364","tid":913731,"uid":12021,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T15:37:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4782ca7b448b32649e12bc78ed7af911d9e09543","tid":913731,"uid":76632,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T15:51:09.000Z","msg":"其實應該大力吸氣，形成真空，等d火無氧自動熄滅。<br />\n<br />\n利申：識真空吸。"},{"pid":"9ae5efc9e2372f0b2b5e6ceb662246f949554ded","tid":913731,"uid":189453,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T15:54:49.000Z","msg":"塵爆前一刻 即係未塵爆 <br />\n咁未塵爆就唔該整熄支蠟燭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39daf9621c17ce97169df0d5ec2ffc0bc400e35e","tid":913731,"uid":117276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T15:55:45.000Z","msg":"唔玩咪冇事囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f2d83638625aa7b01a9a659f809d72e7d33c1e1","tid":913731,"uid":93395,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T16:04:00.000Z","msg":"on9<br />\n真係唔撚識喎你<br />\n轉多幾個圈將d火旋走仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e88ebd00fc6078b1c54f0ec75de33032c2b5fee","tid":913731,"uid":60231,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T16:09:04.000Z","msg":"on9, 平時郁多d隻手，做多d練習，到左喺塵爆前一刻，<br />\n<br />\n即時結四十幾個手印，出水遁 水龍彈之術咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb030dafd6a26b7868ebb1710ec9bc55adb2e75","tid":913731,"uid":153811,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T16:09:06.000Z","msg":"D光差唔多攻到埋你個時大力一吹<br />\n同墮lift前跳一下道理一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後大聲一叫：媽，好辣呀！"},{"pid":"380123ac498574a44d9dd32ee798338fd82ac1ee","tid":913731,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T17:04:16.000Z","msg":"Bu口水出嚟撲火"},{"pid":"bd530bbd21043f31db73a326acedc430b9d62b3b","tid":913731,"uid":89514,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T17:15:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ad8e4746038cb7756ec296f82af3253101ddbaad","tid":913731,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T04:57:46.000Z","msg":"幫樓主呢招改個名<br />\n就叫防塵轉轉離析盾"},{"pid":"d1050db0ab2cc684ad97547d20fd9838c59ca43b","tid":913731,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T05:00:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f08d2e057187882670619480fa0999c6632243c7","tid":913731,"uid":121247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T05:05:38.000Z","msg":"跟我入恒大咪唔洗咁柒囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c87f32d8785ddd30db1d9bf130b1f4ab5fad1d33","tid":913731,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T05:07:20.000Z","msg":"塵爆前一刻走人咪冇事"}]}